      <title>高盛和美国银行正在为厄瓜多尔制定债务互换协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-06/goldman-sachs-bofa-are-working-on-a-new-debt-swap-for-ecuador</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，高盛集团和美国银行正在为一项互换协议做准备，该协议将帮助厄瓜多尔管理其债务融资成本，以换取厄瓜多尔保护部分亚马逊雨林的承诺。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-06/goldman-sachs-bofa-are-working-on-a-new-debt-swap-for-ecuador</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 09:44:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
